                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                     <locus from="41v" to="43v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT3085RepCh365"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለተፈንዎትከ፡ ዘአኮ፡ ለመዓት። ዳዕሙ፡ ለምሕረት።</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                     <note>incorporated with asmat prayer</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i9">
                     <locus from="47r" to="53r"/>
                     <title>Asmat prayer for wealth and against the enemy, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ኃብት፡ ወመግረሬ፡ ፀር።</foreign>, incorporating Image of John, Son of Thunder, Mälk‘a Yoḥannǝs Wäldä Nägwädǝgwad, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መልክአ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልደ፡ ነጐድጓድ፡</foreign>, and the Image of the Trinity, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መልክአ፡ ሥላሴ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ እብ፡ ወወልድ፡. . ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ኃብት፡ ወመግረሬ፡ ፀር።አስማት፡ ዘነገሮ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልደ፡ ነጐድጓድ፡ እንዘ፡ ሀሎ፡ በገነት፡ ከመ፡ ይዕቀብ፡ ሥጋሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል።. . .</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i10">
                     <locus from="53r" to="55r"/>
                     <title>Prayer for the reading of the <title type="complete" ref="LIT2384Taamme"/>, and reading from the <title type="complete" ref="LIT1693John"/>
                     </title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i11">
                     <locus from="56r" to="67r"/>
                     <title>Asmat prayer for Love and Peace, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ፍቅር፡ ወሰላም፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ . . . አአትብ፡ ገጽየ፡ ወኵለንታየ፡ በትምርተ፡ መስቀል፡ ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ፍቅር፡ ወሰላም፡ ከመ፡ አቡነ፡ ዳዊት፡ ወሰሎሞን። በርሃ፡ ፯ጨ፡ ፯ ላሃ፡ . . .</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i12">
