                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">Asmat prayer against the evil eye with the story of Jesus and the disciples at the Sea of Tiberias, Ṣälota Nǝdra, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎተ፡ ንድራ፡</foreign>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
